###
### Lab for Traefik Ingress
###

1. To create the RBAC/grants for Traefik ingress
   kubectl create -f traefik-rbac.yaml

2. To create the traefik daemonset including exposure over NodePort

   kubectl create -f traefik-ds-np.yaml

3. To enable access to the dashboard of Trafeik over nodeport

   kubectl create -f traefik-ui-svc.yaml


4. To deploy the nginxc container color services
  
   kubectl create -f nginxc-black.yml (and the other colors)
  
5. Create services (clusterIP type for above nginxc deployments)

  kubectl expose deployment nginxc-black (for all the colors)

6. Edit (change hostname) ingress rules in tr-ingress.yaml and apply them


   kubectl create -f tr-ingress.yaml


Excercises 


  a) Try to incorporate the q10rv2 service on path /questionnaire

  b) Create more colors (create deployments, change ENV color, create services, adapt tr-ingress.yml)

  c) Try to get hostbased routing in tr-ingress.yml



